but now that we've done that and we have that process in our

5
00:00:17.165 --> 00:00:19.189
heads let's look at some considerations.

6
00:00:19.189 --> 00:00:22.703
Now in one way I modeled how not to do it for you by performing

7
00:00:22.703 --> 00:00:24.783
the upgrade before showing you this stuff.

8
00:00:24.783 --> 00:00:27.377
On the other hand, I thought it was important,

9
00:00:27.377 --> 00:00:30.567
